message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with deep learning-based organ segmentation from medical scans, which is a computer vision problem (cs.CV). The proposed method involves predicting signed distance maps (SDMs) directly from medical scans, which is a machine learning task (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also deals with medical imaging and healthcare applications (cs.MED). Finally, the proposed method involves the use of neural networks, which is a topic in neuroscience and computational neuroscience (cs.NEURON).
